com.facebook.buck.event.external.events

Interface InstallFinishedEventExternalInterface

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BuckEventExternalInterface
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    InstallEvent.Finished

    public interface InstallFinishedEventExternalInterface
extends BuckEventExternalInterface
    Describes an install finished event sent by buck. This type is intended to be used by external applications (like the Intellij Buck plugin) to deserialize events coming from the webserver.
